spec_data.Name: cbmc
spec_data.Description:
CBMC generates traces that demonstrate how an assertion can be violated, or
proves that the assertion cannot be violated within a given number of loop
iterations.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 10 Aug 2017 12:31:01 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Bounded Model Checker for ANSI-C and C++ programs
